 itors\, divorce\, and lawsuits. Long Term Care Planning: How to avoid losi
 ng your life savings. Next Spouse Protection: How to protect your assets f
 rom your surviving spouse’s next spouse. Probate: What is it and how to 
 prevent it. Estate Taxes: What are they\, and how to minimize or eliminate
 . Gifting to Children: How and when to gift your assets and why putting pr
 operty in children’s names may be a mistake. Special Needs: How to provi
 de for special needs (disabled) children and grandchildren. Legacy Plannin
 g: Good planning involves more than money. Learn some powerful tools to he
 lp instill important values in younger generation family membe
